      ''5'')], [(''in_rx'', ''message'', 1), (''in_tx'', ''message'', 1)], [(''out_rx'',
      ''message'', 1), (''out_tx'', ''message'', 1)], ''\n    ARQ Transport Layer.\n    Stop-and-Wait
      ARQ with msg_id, ACKs, and emergency prioritization.\n\n    Upper layer PDU:\n        meta:
